 pulse sequences. Our dynamical decoupling error\ncorrection scheme works for any qubit platform as long as the errors are\nquasistatic.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 16 Oct 2018 18:00:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 17 Jan 2019 19:00:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-01-21"}
