 and millimeter-wavelength detections. These\nresults provide critical constraints for the analysis and interpretation of\nEvent Horizon Telescope data of Sgr A*, M87, and similar sources.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 16 Oct 2018 23:52:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-12-05"}
