ed in the search for\nvector-like quarks at the LHC and, furthermore, we demonstrate that the\nconventional signal channels for vector-like quarks involving the SM Higgs and\ngauge fields are essentially closed in the case of PM.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 17 Oct 2018 13:33:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 17 Dec 2018 15:05:33 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 31 Jan 2019 15:25:52 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 4 Apr 2019 15:08:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-06-26"}
