ion etc.), in the THz regime and on-going works\non tapered wiggler efficiency-enhancement concepts in all optical frequency\nregimes up to X-Rays.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 17 Oct 2018 14:12:44 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 19 Feb 2019 17:38:13 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 23 Apr 2019 11:33:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-04"}
